        <li>Sugar</li>
        <li>Chocolate</li>
        <li>Cocoa Butter</li>
        <li>Milk Fat</li>
        <li>Lecithin (Soy)</li>
        <li>Natural Flavor</li>
    </ul>
    <p>At first glance, none of these ingredients contain gluten. However, it’s important to consider the possibility of cross-contamination during the manufacturing process, especially if the product is made in a facility that also processes gluten-containing foods.</p>

