    <p>Hershey’s has a reputation for being transparent about their manufacturing processes. According to Hershey’s, their Special Dark Chocolate is produced in facilities that also handle gluten-containing ingredients. While the company takes precautions to prevent cross-contamination, there is always a risk, especially for those with severe gluten sensitivities or celiac disease.</p>
    <p>Here’s a breakdown of the potential risks:</p>
